le="font-family:&quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;,Georgia,serif;color:rgb(28,25,53);padding:0 16px;font-weight:500;font-size:28px;line-height:1.2;white-space:nowrap">A reading, on its way</td><td width="18%"><div style="border-top-style:solid;border-top-width:1px;border-color:rgb(196,164,107)"></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(61,54,51);padding:32px 48px 16px 48px;line-height:1.75;font-size:16px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px">Hi Maya,</p><p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px">Thank you for gifting a Soul Blueprint. IвАЩll let River know about it on Friday, December 12 at 9:00 AM, when theyвАЩll receive a short note from me with a private link to claim it and share what I need to read for them.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><div style="padding:16px 48px 0 48px"><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background-color:rgb(245,240,232);border-radius:0.25rem;padding:20px 24px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(122,111,106);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em">The gift</p><p style="font-family:&quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;,Georgia,serif;color:rgb(28,25,53);margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:22px">Soul Blueprint</p><p style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(61,54,51);margin:0;font-size:14px"><span style="color:rgb(122,111,106)">Delivery within 7 days of claim</span>¬†¬Ј¬†<span>$179</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(61,54,51);padding:24px 48px 0 48px;line-height:1.7;font-size:14px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="margin:0">Gifts are non-refundable once payment is complete. Until River opens their link, you can change their name, email, or send date from your gifts page at https://withjosephine.com/my-gifts.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="font-family:&quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;,Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;color:rgb(28,25,53);padding:36px 48px 16px 48px;font-size:22px;line-height:1.4"><tbody><tr><td><p style="margin:0 0 4px 0">With love,</p><p style="margin:0">Josephine вЬ¶</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgb(232,213,196);margin:0"/><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(122,111,106);padding:24px 48px 36px 48px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.7"><tbody><tr><td><p style="margin:0"><a href="mailto:hello@withjosephine.com" style="color:rgb(28,25,53);text-decoration-line:none" target="_blank">hello@withjosephine.com</a>¬†¬Ј¬†<a href="https://withjosephine.com" style="color:rgb(28,25,53);text-decoration-line:none" target="_blank">withjosephine.com</a></p><p style="margin:8px 0 0 0">Readings are offered for entertainment and personal reflection.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><!--/$--></body></html>"`;

